Ultimate‑Stash is my growing collection of games, tools, experiments, and random projects — 
all organized into clean folders with full HTML, data‑URL versions, and shortened HTML. Everything here is built to be simple, fast, and easy to drop into whatever setup you’re using.

---

What’s inside

•  Games (each with full HTML, data‑URL, and fetch versions)
•  Show / media loaders
•  A clean folder system so nothing is messy


---

How it works

Every game folder includes:

• Full‑HTML — the complete code
• Data‑URL — compressed into a single line
• Fetch‑HTML — tiny loader that pulls the full version from GitHub


This makes everything easy to embed, load, or reuse.

